title: What the Heck Happened to Rand Paul?
text:
What the Heck Happened to Rand Paul? What the Heck Happened to Rand Paul? Next Story Prev Story 45 min ago Read more: Roll Call 
Paul has become just another candidate back in the pack, waiting for his inevitable exit. I never expected Kentucky GOP Sen. Rand Paul would win his party's nomination for president, but I did expect he would be a factor in the race. Start the conversation, or Read more at Roll Call.
